Brightis English Translation Patch
Usage and credit terms

This is a fan translation, made for free by people who love the game. It is
not affiliated with Sony or the original developers, and no money changes
hands.

You are welcome to:

- Download the patch and apply it to your own copy of the game.
- Share a link to this project so others can get it the same way.

Please do not:

- Sell this patch, or charge for it in any form.
- Distribute the patch bundled with a copy of the game, or with a
  pre-patched disc image. The patch is delivered on its own, and it does
  nothing without your own legally obtained copy.
- Strip out or alter the credits. If you write about the project or feature
  it somewhere, keep the credited names with it.

The translated text and the work in this repository belong to their authors.
Everything else about the original game belongs to its rights holders.
